                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <addressee>Rev. Mr. Leeser</addressee>\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Dear Friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I send you my lecture of <add>Hebrew</add> last<lb/> with the\n                prayers it is now the last molestation to<lb/> translate it and publish it in the\n                next <sic>numbre</sic><lb/> of the Occident. I wish it, because some very pious<lb/>\n                <sic>jews</sic> here and abroad try unmanly to oppose the union<lb/> of\n                    <placeName>Israel</placeName> and they do so by prejudicing the people\n                against<lb/> me and my words, so they said I have spoken against<lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add> to have <add>Hebrew</add> on <date>Sunday</date>\n                <add>Hebrew</add>. I wish you<lb/> publish this lecture in your next\n                    <sic>numbre</sic>, and prefer<lb/> a note to it, that this lecture was spoken\n                    <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> in <placeName>N.Y.</placeName> on behalf of the\n                convention, rather none<lb/> will read it. If I am done here, I go out west to<lb/>\n                act on the business in <placeName><sic>Cincinaty</sic> Oh.</placeName> though I am\n                sore<lb/> afraid it is in vain, since all the <add>Hebrew</add> heroes are against\n                it</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">I am respectfully yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Dr Wise</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p><placeName>N. Y.</placeName>\n                <date>Sunday</date> morning </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3833nq6t/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
