                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>P. S. I reopened this and took out the lecture for a friend<lb/> who wants to see and\n                translate it, with promise that<lb/> it shall in <sic>faillibly</sic> be\n                    <sic>send</sic> to you by him before<lb/> the <date>10-12<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                    >th</hi></date> of this month.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">Yours</p>"
